{"lemma":"قَلَصِ","slug":"قَلَصِ","root":"ق.ل.ص","root_slug":"ق-ل-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ل-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36153","","n36155","n36156"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to diminish, curtail, constrict"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/qal.la.sˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36153","headword_ar":"قَلَصَ","root":"qlS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, &c.) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quluwSN","text_ar":"قُلُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) [has, among its significations, three which I mention together because two of them are assigned to it in one of the phrases here following, and all of them in another:]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrank;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became contracted"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrunk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, L, Msb, K; *) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ql~S","text_ar":"قلّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, K, *) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoliySN","text_ar":"تَقْلِيصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tql~S","text_ar":"تقلّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M, * Mgh, Msb, * K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotafaEa","text_ar":"اِرْتَفَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [which has two significations:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it rose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became raised:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it went away:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, M, * A, Mgh, Msb, * K; *) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ql~S","text_ar":"قلّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tql~S","text_ar":"تقلّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, Mgh.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSa AlZ~il~u","text_ar":"قَلَصَ الظِّلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ql~S","text_ar":"قلّص"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tql~S","text_ar":"تقلّص"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqlS","text_ar":"اقلص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The shade contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ean~iY","text_ar":"عَنِّى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from me:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"decreased:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went away;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotafaEa","text_ar":"اِرْتَفَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb, TA:) all of which explanations are correct. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSato $afatuhu","text_ar":"قَلَصَتْ شَفَتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His lip became contracted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tql~St","text_ar":"تقلّصت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became contracted upwards."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSa AlD~aroEu","text_ar":"قَلَصَ الضَّرْعُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The udder became drawn together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSa Alv~awobu baEoda Algasoli","text_ar":"قَلَصَ الثَّوْبُ بَعْدَ الغَسْلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrank, after the washing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqamiySu","text_ar":"القَمِيصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ql~S","text_ar":"قلّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoliySN","text_ar":"تَقْلِيصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tql~S","text_ar":"تقلّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The shirt became contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tucked up:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA:) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~iroEu","text_ar":"الدِّرْعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ql~St","text_ar":"قلّصت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tql~St","text_ar":"تقلّصت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the coat of mail became contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] most frequently meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upwards."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(water)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a well,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and became abundant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKtt, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rose"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) in a well; (S;) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotafaEa","text_ar":"اِرْتَفَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M, K:) or, when said of the water of a well, it signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotafaEa","text_ar":"اِرْتَفَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it went away:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it rose by its becoming copious:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) thus it has two contr. significations: and it is also said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSati Albiy^oru","text_ar":"قَلَصَتِ البِيْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the water of the well rose to its upper part:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the well became nearly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"entirely, exhausted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSa Algadiyru","text_ar":"قَلَصَ الغَدِيرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the water of the pool left by a torrent went away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSato nafosuhu","text_ar":"قَلَصَتْ نَفْسُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaloSN","text_ar":"قَلْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaliSato","text_ar":"قَلِصَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) with kesr; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His soul heaved;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became agitated by a tendency to vomit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gavato","text_ar":"غَثَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) and a dial. form thereof is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalasato","text_ar":"قَلَسَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqisato","text_ar":"لَقِسَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSa","text_ar":"قَلَصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quluwSN","text_ar":"قُلُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He leaped, sprang,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bounded."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSati","text_ar":"قَلَصَتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_ibilu","text_ar":"الاـِبِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (so in a copy of the A;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ql~St","text_ar":"قلّصت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoliySN","text_ar":"تَقْلِيصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) [probably signify the same: or] the former signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels rose in their pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the camels)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active, and quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were vigorous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$am~arato","text_ar":"شَمَّرَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) in their pace, or going: (M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went on in one regular, uniform,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constant, course."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSa","text_ar":"قَلَصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quluwSN","text_ar":"قُلُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went away;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IB, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ql~S","text_ar":"قلّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoliySN","text_ar":"تَقْلِيصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) each likewise signifies the same, but the latter in an intensive sense, said of tears; and so the latter when said of anything: (TA:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tql~S","text_ar":"تقلّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of an animal's milk. (Mgh.) ―         -b7-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSa Alqawomu","text_ar":"قَلَصَ القَوْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quluwSN","text_ar":"قُلُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The company of men took up their luggage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TS, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collected themselves together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and went,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"departed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TS, L, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they became distant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remote:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"migrated, quickly"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the dwelling. (A, TA.) ―         -b8-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSa AlgulaAmu","text_ar":"قَلَصَ الغُلَامُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The boy grew up and walked."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaluwSN","text_ar":"قَلُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","A","Mgh","TA","Fr","IKtt","O","TS","L"]},{"entry_id":"n36155","headword_ar":"قَلْصٌ","root":"qlS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Abundance"},{"kind":"text","text":"of water: and, contr.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"paucity"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSapN","text_ar":"قَلَصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaloSapN","text_ar":"قَلْصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"have the former of these significations: (M:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSapN","text_ar":"قَلَصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a well"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collecting"},{"kind":"text","text":"therein"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and rising:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaloSapN","text_ar":"قَلْصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to some lexicologists, as mentioned by Ibn-El-Ajdábee: (IB:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSapN","text_ar":"قَلَصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSaAtN","text_ar":"قَلَصَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) and the pl. [or rather quasi-pl. n.] of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaloSapN","text_ar":"قَلْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSN","text_ar":"قَلَصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IB.) An Arab of the desert is related to have said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlmaA'i","text_ar":"مِنَ المَاءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"famaA wajadotu fiyhaA A_il~aA qaloSapF","text_ar":"فَمَا وَجَدْتُ فِيهَا اـِلَّا قَلْصَةً","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And I found not in it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. the well]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"save a little quantity of water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","M","S","K","IB"]},{"entry_id":"n36156","headword_ar":"قَلَصٌ","root":"qlS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaloSN","text_ar":"قَلْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beginning of"},{"kind":"text","text":"a she-camel's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becoming fat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quluwSN","text_ar":"قُلُوصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) See 4."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}